data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! LISTING INCLUDES ALL APPLIANCES WITH WASHER, DRYER AND HOT TUB! Welcome home to this beautifully maintained home in The Heights of Saengerhalle. This perfect family home features 4 bedrooms, 2 and a half baths with a loft and office space. The floor plan is ideal with the master bedroom downstairs and kitchen open to the dining and living room. The kitchen is wonderful with stainless steel appliances that all convey as well as granite countertops and ample cabinet space.The washer and dryer will also convey. Just in time for football season, the backyard is an entertainers paradise. The extended porch houses a large hot tub and deck! Three great sized bedrooms and loft are upstairs as well as another full bath. Make this one yours and schedule your showing today!
